DataElement.preferredName: Lowest Fibrinogen Level Laboratory Procedure Outcome 1 Decimal Place Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The 1 decimal place numeric laboratory value measured, assigned or computed related to the assessment of the lowest Fibrinogen level.
